If you do it this way in the long term,

123
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,879
The rotator cuff will be overloaded.

124
00:11:25,639 --> 00:11:26,799
Furthermore, from what I have observed,

125
00:11:27,559 --> 00:11:28,519
your symptoms

126
