230
00:19:47,920 --> 00:19:48,680
Please, I beg you

231
00:19:48,680 --> 00:19:49,559
Don't give me a bad review

232
00:19:49,559 --> 00:19:50,200
Lárgate

233
00:20:07,039 --> 00:20:07,599
Li Youen

234
00:20:07,599 --> 00:20:08,640
I've been waiting for you for a long time

235
00:20:08,759 --> 00:20:09,720
You're moving, right?

236
00:20:09,720 --> 00:20:10,880
Did you think we wouldn't find you?

237
00:20:11,200 --> 00:20:12,839
