245
00:21:01,599 --> 00:21:03,599
His internal organs have symptoms of bleeding.

246
00:21:04,160 --> 00:21:05,319
He needs surgery as soon as possible.

247
00:21:05,599 --> 00:21:07,759
You will also have to stay in the hospital for observation for a while.

248
00:21:10,200 --> 00:21:11,240
It must be saved.

249
00:21:11,240 --> 00:21:12,079
After my parents left,

250
00:21:12,480 --> 00:21:14,119
He is my only relative.

251
00:21:14,799 --> 00:21:15,640
I beg you,

252
00:21:16,440 --> 00:21:17,559
