280
00:22:58,359 --> 00:22:59,079
Do you hear?

281
00:23:02,279 --> 00:23:03,000
Oh!

282
00:23:04,839 --> 00:23:05,839
I don't want to be cured anymore.

283
00:23:08,880 --> 00:23:10,000
