284
00:23:11,240 --> 00:23:13,079
Little You next door was taken away today.

285
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:16,839
It is already the third this year.

286
00:23:16,839 --> 00:23:18,240
That is leaving my side.

287
00:23:21,400 --> 00:23:22,880
